# idd-merge-loop durable state.
#
# Only the loop's continuity files are committed, so a fresh process / cold
# restart resumes from disk with zero loss. Everything else here is transient:
# per-run runner logs (ralph-run-*.log), runtime sentinels (DONE / STOP /
# NEEDS-HUMAN), and the orchestrator's per-slice audit intermediates
# (0{1,2,3,4}_*.md) — those stay untracked (audit trail, not source).
*
!.gitignore
!backlog.md
!loop_state.md
!HANDOFF.md
